| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2493 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f3c9a59-4fc3-51e7-bfff-5dda7d6e365a"
